<h1>Installing Velocity</h1>
<p>To install Velocity on most platforms simple run the velocity-install.jar
by double-clicking on the file or running 'java -jar velocity-install.jar' from
the command line. Follow the instructions in the installer.</p>
<h2>Windows Vista Installation</h2>
<p>The Velocity installer will install Velocity to C:\Program Files\ by
default on Windows operating systems. Windows Vista, however, will not allow
applications to write to the Program Files folder without elevated (admin)
privileges.</p>
